snippet.title: Remember the Children | Kyle Pederson
snippet.description:
Remember the Children. Composed by Kyle Pederson for SATB Voices with Piano and Djembe.

https://www.giamusic.com/store/resour...

Lyrics

Mama hears you cryin’ as you try to keep it inside, 
as you want to wear a brave face to the world.
Mama hears you prayin’ as you say goodnight and lay there, 
as you bare your soul to God and seek your place in this world.

Papa hears you playin’ when you think no one’s payin’ attention, 
when there is no mention of tears, and you’re free to laugh.
Papa sees you dreamin’ of a new day of freedom 
for a new way of being a child in this world.

Mama nakusikia unalia, mtoto 
(Mama hears you crying, child)
Mama anakuombea 
(Mama prays for you)
Mama ana matumaini kwako mtoto 
(Mama hopes for you, child) 
Je, ulimwengu utasikiliza ndoto za watoto wake? 
(Will the world listen to the dreams of her children?)
Tukumbuke watoto 
(Remember the children)

#WaltonMusic #Choir #Choral
